title: Fine Sweeper v1.2.1.104
description: Fine Sweeper is a re-envisioning of the good old casual game wee all familiar with since Windows 3.11 came along, and we collectively sunk millions of productive hours into an ugly little thing called Minesweeper. Still itching for a fix but you can look at the hopelessly outdated and functional presentation any more?
